# Data (never commit patient data)
data/
*.nii
*.nii.gz
*.dcm
jwave_test/results/phase4_pilot_dataset/
# Rescaled/smoothed masks + contours derived directly from real ACDC
# patient anatomy (patient001/023) -- same caution as phase4_pilot_dataset,
# even though these are abstracted to a toy domain scale.
jwave_test/results/mri_irregular_ring_*.npz
jwave_test/results/mri_motion_cycle_*.npz

# jwave_ring_tomography: same caution -- ray/timing/amplitude arrays
# derived directly from real ACDC patient anatomy (patient001/023).
# Figures (PNGs) derived from this data are fine to commit, matching
# jwave_test's own precedent; only the raw derived arrays are excluded.
jwave_ring_tomography/results/*.npz

# Colab working notebooks: the packaged zip (and the notebook itself,
# which embeds that same package as base64 to work around a broken
# upload widget) both contain copies of mri_motion_cycle_patient001/023
# -- same real-ACDC-patient-data caution as above, just in a form the
# filename-based rules can't catch (a zip / base64 blob, not a bare
# .npz). Session-local working artifacts, not meant for the repo.
jwave_ring_tomography/notebooks/

